# 🎯 Why This Happens

👉 Very important concept:

> **ODF upgrade is NOT only driven by Subscription**

Even though `odf-operator` upgraded:

👉 The **rest of stack upgrades only when StorageCluster reconciles**

---

# 🔥 Root Cause

Your cluster is in this state:

```text
ODF operator → upgraded ✅
StorageCluster → NOT reconciled ❌
```

So:

* ODF operator is new (4.20)
* But it hasn’t upgraded internal components yet

