### 2. Or ODF waiting for safe upgrade

---

# 🔥 Step 2 — Check Ceph health (VERY IMPORTANT)

Run:

```bash
oc get cephcluster -n openshift-storage -o jsonpath='{.items[*].status.ceph.health}'
```

👉 Expected:

```text
HEALTH_OK
```

---

If you see:

* `HEALTH_WARN`
* `HEALTH_ERR`

👉 ODF will NOT upgrade further ❗

---

# 🔄 Step 3 — Force reconcile (if needed)

Sometimes reconciliation is slow.

Trigger manually:

```bash
oc annotate storagecluster ocs-storagecluster \
-n openshift-storage \
odf.openshift.io/force-reconcile="$(date +%s)" --overwrite
```

